---
title: Smokey Chicken Strips with Lemon Pepper Potatoes & Cos Salad
description: We’re officially making chicken strips tonight, so don’t be afraid to break out your best chicken dance! We recommend drizzling over the delicious garlic aioli, but if you need to grab ‘em and dunk ‘em, we won’t tell anyone. Promise.
